            <paragraph>You can use <strong>Bone2D</strong> and <reference internal="True" refuri="class_skeleton2d#class-skeleton2d"><inline classes="std std-ref">Skeleton2D</inline></reference> nodes to animate 2D meshes created with the <reference internal="True" refuri="class_polygon2d#class-polygon2d"><inline classes="std std-ref">Polygon2D</inline></reference> UV editor.</paragraph>
